name: WaWa's "Best of" Cube (Vintage+Power)
description:
This cube is intended to provide a variety of powerful draft decks for exciting games. This cube relies on proxies to ensure it can be assembled for around $200.

Archetypes: 

{w}{u} Flying Control
{b}{u} Saboteurs
{r}{g} Dragons
{w}{g} Lifegain
{w}{b} Angels
{r}{w} Equipment
{b}{r} Discard/Aggro
{g}{b} Mill/Reanimator
{r}{u} Spellslinger Prowess
{g}{u} Ramp/Control

Cube Highlights:

-Includes Mox artifacts
-8/9 "Power 9" Cards (Minus Time Walk)
-Complete set of Dual Lands and Fetchlands 

Please leave a comment if you have any suggestions!
